herst]]\n|\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Defenceman|D]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |2\n|[[Oskari Laaksonen]]\n|{{flagicon|FIN}} [[Ilves|Tampereen Ilves]]\n|[[Buffalo Sabres]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Defenceman|D]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |3\n|[[Toni Utunen]]\n|{{flagicon|FIN}} [[Tappara|Tappara Tampere]]\n|[[Vancouver Canucks]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Defenceman|D]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |7\n|[[Urho Vaakanainen]] '''\"A\"'''\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Providence Bruins]]\n| [[Boston Bruins]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Defenceman|D]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |15\n|[[Henri Jokiharju]] '''\"A\"'''\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Buffalo Sabres]]\n| [[Buffalo Sabres]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Defenceman|D]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |21\n|[[Otto Latvala]]\n|{{flagicon|FIN}} [[Lemp\u00e4\u00e4l\u00e4n Kisa|LeKi Lemp\u00e4\u00e4l\u00e4]]\n| \n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Defenceman|D]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |34\n|[[Ville Heinola]]\n|{{flagicon|FIN}} [[Lukko|Rauman Lukko]]\n| [[Winnipeg Jets]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Defenceman|D]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |36\n|[[Anttoni Honka]]\n|{{flagicon|FIN}} [[JYP Jyv\u00e4skyl\u00e4]]\n| [[Carolina Hurricanes]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Forward (ice hockey)|F]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |10\n|[[Aleksi Heponiemi]]\n|{{flagicon|FIN}} [[Oulun K\u00e4rp\u00e4t]]\n| [[Florida Panthers]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Forward (ice hockey)|F]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |12\n|[[Samuli Vainionp\u00e4\u00e4]]\n|{{flagicon|FIN}} [[Ilves|Tampereen Ilves]]\n|\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Forward (ice hockey)|F]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |13\n|[[Valtteri Puustinen]]\n|{{flagicon|FIN}} [[HPK|HPK H\u00e4meenlinna]]\n| [[Pittsburgh Penguins]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |[[Forward (ice hockey)|F]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" |18\n|[[Teemu Engberg]]\n|{{flagicon|FIN