DFDF;\"| [[Milwaukee IndyFest|MIL]]<br>{{small|2}}\n|style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| [[Detroit Indy Grand Prix|DET]]<br>{{small|2}}\n|style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| [[Grand Prix of Portland|POR]]<br>{{small|2}}\n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Grand Prix of Cleveland|CLE]]<br>{{small|20}}\n|style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[Honda Indy Toronto|TOR]]<br>{{small|3}}\n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Firestone Indy 400|MCH]]<br>{{small|10}}\n|style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[Honda Indy 200|MDO]]<br>{{small|3}}\n|style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| '''''[[New England Indy 200|NHA]]'''''<br>{{small|3*}}\n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Molson Indy Vancouver|VAN]]<br>{{small|9}}\n|style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[Champ Car Grand Prix of Road America|ROA]]<br>{{small|3}}\n|style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| '''''[[Firestone Indy 225|NAZ]]'''''<br>{{small|3}}\n|style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"| [[Mazda Raceway Laguna Seca|LAG]]<br>{{small|4}}\n!\n|rowspan=2 style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| '''2nd'''\n|rowspan=2 style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| '''178'''\n|-\n! [[Mercedes-Benz in motorsport|Mercedes-Benz]] 500I [[V8 engine|V8]][[Turbocharger|t]]\n|colspan=3|\n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| ''[[1994 Indianapolis 500|INDY]]''<br><small>17*</small>\n|colspan=12|\n!\n|-\n| [[1995 PPG Indy Car World Series|1995]]\n! [[Team Penske]]\n! [[Penske Racing|Penske]] PC-24\n! [[Mercedes-Benz in motorsport|Mercedes-Benz]] IC108B [[V8 engine|V8]][[Turbocharger|t]]\n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Homestead\u2013Miami Indy 300|MIA]]<br>{{small|24}} \n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[1995 Indycar Australia|SRF]]<br>{{small|18}} \n|style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| ''[[XM Satellite Radio Indy 200|PHX]]''<br>{{small|3*}} \n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Grand Prix of Long Beach|LBH]]<br>{{small|20}} \n|style=\"background:#FFFFBF;\"| ''[[Firestone Indy 225|NAZ]]''<br>{{small|1}} \n|style=\"background:#FFCFCF;\"| [[1995 Indianapolis 500|INDY]]<br>{{small|DNQ}}\n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Milwaukee 