cing]]\n! [[March Engineering|March]] 85C\n! [[Cosworth]] [[Cosworth DFV#DFX|DFX]] [[V8 engine|V8]][[Turbocharger|t]]\n|style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| [[Grand Prix of Long Beach|LBH]]<br>{{small|2}}\n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[1985 Indianapolis 500|INDY]]<br>{{small|13}}\n|style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"| [[Milwaukee IndyFest|MIL]]<br>{{small|8}}\n|style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[Grand Prix of Portland|POR]]<br>{{small|3}}\n|style=\"background:#DFDFDF;\"| [[Meadowlands Grand Prix|MEA]]<br>{{small|2}}\n|style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"| [[Grand Prix of Cleveland|CLE]]<br>{{small|8}}\n|style=\"background:#FFFFBF;\"| [[Firestone Indy 400|MCH]]<br>{{small|1}}\n|style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"| [[Champ Car Grand Prix of Road America|ROA]]<br>{{small|5}}\n|style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"| [[Pocono IndyCar 400|POC]]<br>{{small|6}}\n|style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"| [[Honda Indy 200|MDO]]<br>{{small|8}}\n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Grand Prix of Montreal|SAN]]<br>{{small|25}}\n|style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[Firestone Indy 400|MCH]]<br>{{small|13}}\n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Mazda Raceway Laguna Seca|LAG]]<br>{{small|24}}\n|style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"| [[XM Satellite Radio Indy 200|PHX]]<br>{{small|8}}\n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Tamiami Park|MIA]]<br>{{small|26}}\n! !!\n|style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"| '''6th'''\n|style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"| '''104'''\n|-\n| [[1986 CART PPG Indy Car World Series|1986]]\n! [[Patrick Racing]]\n! [[March Engineering|March]] 86C\n! [[Cosworth]] [[Cosworth DFV#DFX|DFX]] [[V8 engine|V8]][[Turbocharger|t]]\n|style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[XM Satellite Radio Indy 200|PHX]]<br>{{small|3}}\n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Grand Prix of Long Beach|LBH]]<br>{{small|16}}\n|style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"| [[1986 Indianapolis 500|INDY]]<br>{{small|7}}\n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Milwaukee IndyFest|MIL]]<br>{{small|24}}\n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| '''[[Grand Prix of Portland|POR]]'''<br>{{small|12}}\n|style=\"backgro